user.biography: The official Instagram of Naughty Dog, developers of The Last of Us Part II, available now on PS4. Games rated RP to M by the ESRB.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Naughty Dog on August 02, 2021.

node.text:
Thank you to Tumblr user ssdivinorum for sharing your The Last of Us Part II-inspired black and grey tattoo 🌿🖤 We're loving the beautiful work and detail, and we're honored that you celebrated the 1-year anniversary with this gorgeous piece!⁣
⁣
Share your own tattoos, fan art, and more here: https://naughty-dog.tumblr.com/ugc

node.text:

node.text: Pack your bags for global adventures with Nathan and Chloe -- no passport required! ✈️ Pick up Uncharted 4 and Uncharted: The Lost Legacy 50% off with @PlayStation's Summer Sale!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Naughty Dog on July 21, 2021. May be an anime-style image of text.

node.text: Whether you want to find every Precursor Orb or race your way to glory, the Jak and Daxter Bundle's got you covered! Experience every Jak and Daxter game in this ultimate collection for 50% off with PlayStation's Summer Sale on PSN!
